data.description: Great opportunity to buy a one acre horse property and home on the South end of Carson City. Close to shopping and restaurants. Easy access to the 580 Freeway and Hwy 50 to Lake Tahoe. This lovely two bedroom and one bath home boasts hardwood flooring in the kitchen and dining room. Kitchen has granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. There is a large utility room/laundry room with plenty of storage room. There are two 10 x 12 Sheds, plenty of room for your RV and Toys and room to build a garage or shop.
